This paper is likely to belong to the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) as it deals with a variant of first-order logic. It could also belong to Programming Languages (cs.PL) as nominal logic is used in programming language theory. Additionally, it could be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.LG) as nominal logic has been used in the development of machine learning algorithms. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is another possible category as nominal logic has been used in knowledge representation and reasoning. Finally, Software Engineering (cs.SE) is a possible category as nominal logic has been used in the verification of software systems.
